00:20:02.666 --> 00:20:05.106
identify who's at the highest risk.

350
00:20:06.726 --> 00:20:06.826
The

351
00:20:07.746 --> 00:20:10.986
application of interception approaches is going to depend on a cost-benefit

352
00:20:11.026 --> 00:20:13.066
analysis. What are the side effects of the approach?

353
00:20:13.576 --> 00:20:17.286
The vaccines have an advantage that they have very minimal side effects, so you

354
00:20:17.326 --> 00:20:20.866
might think about applying those to a broader population, which is exciting.

